      "contradicting_evidence": ["Latest published 7-day MA was only ~4.71 (May 31), far below the 60 threshold (https://en.macromicro.me/series/30932/imf-hormuz-number-total-ma7)", "Three months of paralysis with the Strait described as a 'ghost route' and no reopening agreement (https://gulfnews.com/world/mena/three-months-of-paralysis-strait-of-hormuz-remains-a-ghost-route-1.500560668)"]
    },
    {
